%global commit          78cd7a343bde765feaecace9f575518435d13e11

%gometa

%global common_description %{expand:
The Go mobile repository holds packages and build tools for using Go on mobile
platforms.}

%global golicenses      LICENSE PATENTS
%global godocs          doc example AUTHORS CONTRIBUTING.md CONTRIBUTORS README.md

Name:           %{goname}
Version:        0
Release:        %autorelease
Summary:        Go support for Mobile devices

# Upstream license specification: BSD-3-Clause
# Automatically converted from old format: BSD - review is highly recommended.
